saat kau menceritakan kisahmu tempo hari.

91
00:07:45,646 --> 00:07:47,482
Kau pasti sakit hati.

92
00:07:51,110 --> 00:07:51,944
Maaf.

93
00:07:56,032 --> 00:07:57,033
Aku ingin...

94
00:07:59,827 --> 00:08:01,621
hidup sebagai pejuang.

95
00:08:05,249 --> 00:08:06,876
Aku membohongi kakekku,

96
00:08:08,169 --> 00:08:10,254
membuat bibiku cemas,

97
00:08:11,589 --> 00:08:14,634
dan menjadi beban
bagi orang yang setia kepadaku.

98
00:08:17,053 --> 00:08:19,430
Tapi aku menyemangati diriku...

99
00:08:21,474 --> 00:08:23,226
dengan meyakini bahwa ini benar.

100
00:08:24,435 --> 00:08:25,436
Namun...

101
00:08:30,733 --> 00:08:32,985
setelah mendengar kisahmu,

102
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:36,239
duniaku hancur.

103
00:08:39,283 --> 00:08:40,785
Selama kebersamaan kita,

104
00:08:42,245 --> 00:08:45,331
aku tak pernah memikirkan asal-usulmu.

105
00:08:47,708 --> 00:08:49,377
Jika dipikir-pikir,

106
00:08:50,545 --> 00:08:52,797
aku hanya beranggapan
kau adalah bangsawan.

107
00:09:01,889 --> 00:09:04,809
Aku mengira diriku berbeda
dari bangsawan lain.

108
00:09:06,727 --> 00:09:07,979
Tapi ternyata tidak.

109
00:09:09,897 --> 00:09:12,567
Tujuanku berjuang tampak ironis.

110
00:09:15,987 --> 00:09:17,238
Aku tetaplah

111
00:09:20,199 --> 00:09:23,077
gadis bangsawan manja...

112
00:09:26,664 --> 00:09:29,208
yang belum mampu keluar dari tandunya.

113
00:09:32,587 --> 00:09:33,588
Jadi...

114
00:09:36,382 --> 00:09:37,884
aku minta satu hal.

115
00:09:42,930 --> 00:09:44,265
Tolong jangan sakit hati.

116
00:10:39,362 --> 00:10:41,238
Kau sudah melangkah maju.

117
00:10:42,448 --> 00:10:43,908
Ini hanya...

118
00:10:45,493 --> 00:10:46,786
rintangan kecil.

119
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,509
Kau harus terus maju.

120
00:11:03,052 --> 00:11:04,512
Aku akan melangkah mundur.

121
00:11:07,223 --> 00:11:09,433
Bukan karena statusmu yang tinggi.

122
00:11:10,226 --> 00:11:12,603
Kau bisa saja memilih diam.

123
00:11:13,688 --> 00:11:15,731
Kau bisa saja mengabaikannya.

124
00:11:19,276 --> 00:11:21,570
Tapi di sini kau menangis.
Karena itu, aku mundur.

125
00:11:26,409 --> 00:11:27,576
Di dunia ini...

126
00:11:30,204 --> 00:11:31,872
perbedaan memang ada.

127
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,083
Perbedaan kekuasaan.

128
00:11:35,292 --> 00:11:36,544
Perbedaan pendapat.

129
00:11:40,589 --> 00:11:41,757
Perbedaan status sosial.

130
00:11:43,926 --> 00:11:45,553
Tapi itu bukan salahmu.

131
00:11:46,429 --> 00:11:48,013
Bukan pula salahku.

132
00:11:49,265 --> 00:11:50,891
Hanya saja kita telah bertemu...

133
00:11:54,770 --> 00:11:56,147
di dunia seperti ini.

134
00:12:04,321 --> 00:12:05,489
Di Joseon-mu

135
00:12:06,365 --> 00:12:07,908
ada Pak Haengrang

136
00:12:08,743 --> 00:12:10,327
dan Bu Haman.

137
00:12:11,954 --> 00:12:15,708
Sama halnya dengan pemburu budak,
pembuat tembikar, juru bahasa,

138
00:12:16,542 --> 00:12:18,669
dan bahkan pesuruh.

139
00:12:21,714 --> 00:12:23,340
Maka jadilah pejuang.

140
00:12:26,093 --> 00:12:27,720
Tapi jangan lupa, kau Nona Ae-sin.

141
00:12:28,304 --> 00:12:29,805
Itu pilihan lebih bijak dan aman.

142
00:12:34,602 --> 00:12:36,187
Bertahanlah dari kekacauan ini.

143
00:12:38,564 --> 00:12:40,274
Hiduplah selama mungkin

144
00:12:41,776 --> 00:12:43,778
dan lindungi Joseon-mu.

145
00:12:53,162 --> 00:12:55,206
Simpanlah itu.

146
00:12:58,125 --> 00:12:59,835
Sebaiknya jangan bepergian lagi.

147
00:13:42,378 --> 00:13:44,046
Pipimu masih utuh.

148
00:13:44,964 --> 00:13:46,715
Kudengar tamparannya cukup keras.

149
00:13:48,092 --> 00:13:50,469
Aku tak terbiasa dipukul orang,

150
00:13:50,553 --> 00:13:51,804
jadi, terasa menyakitkan.

151
00:13:53,681 --> 00:13:55,182
Kenapa kau ditampar?

152
00:14:01,605 --> 00:14:03,691
<i>Aku menembak burung hitam</i>

153
00:14:04,859 --> 00:14:06,610
supaya tak bisa terbang lagi.

154
00:14:08,445 --> 00:14:09,280
Burung hitam?

155
00:14:11,282 --> 00:14:13,159
Tampar aku kalau kau mau juga.

156
00:14:13,993 --> 00:14:15,452
Aku dengar Gui-dan ketahuan.

157
00:14:16,203 --> 00:14:18,330
Jangan terlalu naif.

158
00:14:18,706 --> 00:14:20,457
Tamparan tak akan bisa menebusnya,

159
00:14:21,041 --> 00:14:22,626
jadi, anggap kau berutang budi.

160
00:14:22,877 --> 00:14:24,420
Dia bilang ibunya sakit.

161
00:14:24,503 --> 00:14:27,214
Rasa bakti kepada ibunya cukup indah.

162
00:14:27,798 --> 00:14:29,049
Aku sampai menangis.

163
00:14:29,133 --> 00:14:31,093
Kalau tak mau menangis sungguhan,

164
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:33,596
jauhi orang-orangku.

165
00:14:34,096 --> 00:14:35,347
Aku tak bisa walau ingin.

166
00:14:36,015 --> 00:14:38,017
Mereka tak bisa bekerja dengan benar

167
00:14:38,601 --> 00:14:40,352
dan gadis baru itu

168
00:14:40,603 --> 00:14:42,521
sudah berpihak kepada lawan.

169
00:14:45,024 --> 00:14:46,192
Aku sakit hati.

170
00:14:46,650 --> 00:14:49,195
Dahulu aku bahkan mencemaskan adiknya.

171
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:56,619
- Situasi di sini aman?
- Ya.

172
00:14:56,702 --> 00:14:58,829
Para tamu menggemari kopi karena salju.

173
00:14:59,288 --> 00:15:00,289
Begitu.

174
00:15:01,749 --> 00:15:02,750
Selamat datang...

175
00:15:13,219 --> 00:15:14,303
Sial.

176
00:15:21,852 --> 00:15:26,315
Lama tak bertemu, Dokter Matsuyama.

177
00:15:26,398 --> 00:15:28,984
Ya, sudah lama, Nona Kudo.

178
00:15:29,902 --> 00:15:31,904
Aku tak tahu Anda ada di Joseon.

179
00:15:31,987 --> 00:15:33,405
Ini berkat Rinoie.

180
00:15:34,198 --> 00:15:38,077
Dia merekomendasikanku
ke Pusat Pengobatan Hanseong

181
00:15:38,160 --> 00:15:40,746
sebagai ahli bedah mereka.

182
00:15:40,955 --> 00:15:42,873
Kau harus mampir sesekali.

183
00:15:45,042 --> 00:15:48,295
Bukan berarti aku mengharapkanmu sakit.

184
00:15:51,048 --> 00:15:52,216
Rupanya begitu.

185
00:15:53,259 --> 00:15:54,969
Omong-omong,

186
00:15:56,053 --> 00:15:57,721
kenapa Rinoie melakukan itu?

187
00:15:58,847 --> 00:16:00,933
Karena laporan autopsi yang kuterima.

188
00:16:01,809 --> 00:16:04,520
Laporan autopsi itu menyatakan

189
00:16:05,104 --> 00:16:08,065
penyebab sebenarnya kematian

190
00:16:09,775 --> 00:16:11,568
suamimu.

191
00:16:15,614 --> 00:16:18,284
Yang menggerakkan Tuan Rinoie

192
00:16:18,367 --> 00:16:20,286
adalah sisi kebenaran,

193
00:16:20,536 --> 00:16:22,121
Nona Kudo.

194
00:16:24,373 --> 00:16:25,916
Baik kalau begitu.

195
00:16:27,042 --> 00:16:28,836
Ini tak akan menguntungkanku.

196
00:16:32,715 --> 00:16:34,591
<i>Mungkin karena usianya yang muda.</i>

197
00:16:35,801 --> 00:16:37,261
Dia cepat pulih.

198
00:16:37,845 --> 00:16:39,847
Dia bisa keluar kira-kira pekan depan.

199
00:16:40,431 --> 00:16:42,766
Bersihkan lukanya setiap jam.

200
00:16:43,392 --> 00:16:44,226
Baik, Pak.

201
00:16:46,020 --> 00:16:47,396
Dia cepat pulih.

202
00:16:47,646 --> 00:16:49,398
Dia boleh pulang sekitar pekan depan.

203
00:16:49,481 --> 00:16:51,108
Sungguh?

204
00:16:51,984 --> 00:16:53,610
Astaga, kau tak akan mati.

205
00:16:53,694 --> 00:16:54,945
Sungguh melegakan.

206
00:16:56,488 --> 00:16:58,782
Tapi kau siapa?

207
00:17:00,034 --> 00:17:01,577
Kenapa aku di sini?

208
00:17:04,204 --> 00:17:05,164
Soon-sim.

209
00:17:05,247 --> 00:17:08,792
Kau di rumah sakit paling maju di Joseon.

210
00:17:09,376 --> 00:17:10,336
Seorang pria...

211
00:17:10,919 --> 00:17:13,297
meminta kami merawatmu.

212
00:17:14,298 --> 00:17:17,760
Dia membayar semuanya
termasuk operasi luka tembakmu,

213
00:17:17,843 --> 00:17:20,387
setiap makananmu,

214
00:17:20,471 --> 00:17:22,514
dan obat yang kau minum.

215
00:17:22,806 --> 00:17:24,683
Kau hanya perlu sembuh.

216
00:17:25,267 --> 00:17:26,185
Paham?

217
00:17:27,227 --> 00:17:28,937
Kenapa kalian baik sekali kepadaku?

218
00:17:29,021 --> 00:17:31,148
Kau tak dengar ucapan kami?

219
00:17:31,231 --> 00:17:32,816
Kau hanya perlu sembuh.

220
00:17:32,900 --> 00:17:34,818
Terdengar tak masuk akal.

221
00:17:36,779 --> 00:17:39,448
Kenapa orang mau menolongku tanpa imbalan?

222
00:17:44,495 --> 00:17:45,412
Nak.

223
00:17:46,038 --> 00:17:49,208
Kau mungkin tak terbiasa
karena dunia yang kau tinggali,

224
00:17:49,541 --> 00:17:51,460
tapi orang dewasa

225
00:17:51,543 --> 00:17:53,629
harus menolong anak-anak
meski tanpa imbalan.

226
00:17:55,798 --> 00:17:58,675
- Pikirkan kesembuhanmu saja, ya?
- Benar.

227
00:17:59,593 --> 00:18:01,428
Siapakah pria

228
00:18:01,845 --> 00:18:03,263
yang menjagaku?

229
00:18:03,347 --> 00:18:06,183
Dia banyak bertanya tentang dirimu

230
00:18:06,266 --> 00:18:08,852
dan kenapa kau menolongnya.

231
00:18:08,936 --> 00:18:10,062
Tapi jangan khawatir.

232
00:18:10,145 --> 00:18:12,022
Kami tak bilang apa pun.

233
00:18:12,106 --> 00:18:14,483
Kami tetap bungkam.

234
00:18:15,109 --> 00:18:16,902
Kenapa harus dirahasiakan?

235
00:18:17,569 --> 00:18:20,239
Perbuatan baik harus dilakukan diam-diam.

236
00:18:20,322 --> 00:18:23,033
Jangan sampai tangan kanan
mengetahui perbuatan tangan kiri.

237
00:18:24,576 --> 00:18:26,036
Ada satu kisah mengharukan

238
00:18:26,120 --> 00:18:28,122
tentang anak kecil di peti
yang kuselamatkan.

239
00:18:28,205 --> 00:18:30,791
Aku melakukannya agar tampak keren.

240
00:18:33,794 --> 00:18:35,170
